description: Token Rupiah Elektronik yang dijamin nilainya 1:1 dengan saldo penjamin yang diendapkan di rekening PT LUMBUNG MOMENTUM BANGSA. Diaudit secara berkala oleh akuntan publik.
top_6_features: No ICO, no premine, no reserved, no Developer's cut.
Consensus via Delegate Proof of Stake (Fast Paxos)
High bandwidth, averaging 2000 Transactions per Second
Purely decentralized and powered by community's economic activities
Organic demands and guaranteed growth as long as people still eat food.
